## Screens & Features

### Course Feature
- Displays essays, summaries, prompts, and Practice/Habit instructions for current stage
- Content pulled from `StageContent` model, hosted on the Squarespace CMS
- Features:
  - “Mark as Read”
  - Journal links
  - Stage metadata
  - Drip-feed option

